reviewText: I used to watch this about... 11 or 12 years ago when i was 4 or 5. I loved it! I had forgotten about it until recently, so I looked it up on the net, and got a bunch of pictures and stuff on it. I can't believe they took it off the air. Whoever created it was a genius and I hope it comes back soon. LUV U MR. SQUISHINGTON <3
